{
  "_doc": "DIAGNOSTIC: classical KL-KD (no ZAR, no RRDSD). If this runs fine, the problem is in my RRDSD code. If this ALSO stalls, it's system-level (OneDrive sync, disk I/O, etc). Same warm-start + kill rules + schedule as r1b for comparability.",

